Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:37.98,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.63,0:00:39.51,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.21,0:00:44.36,CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集 怎麼了 請回答
