Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.03,0:02:03.70,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\3c&H8EC9DA&\c&HEAFCFD&}用冷酷的話刺傷你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.72,0:02:09.20,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFDFCDE&\2c&HBAB56A&\3c&HADB063&}就算全世界都不再信任你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:15.16,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HFDFFD4&\3c&HC0B660&}給你扣上荊棘的王冠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:20.95,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HF6F3D8&\3c&HAED256&}我依然只站在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.03,0:02:26.53,op_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\c&HF2EEDE&\3c&HBB9D62&}因為我能體會你的孤獨和痛苦
