Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:25.97,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,500)\an2}你不再愛我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.21,0:21:32.49,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}也不再需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:41.11,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}徒留我一人 孤零零在原地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.92,0:21:49.21,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}當初你說過什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.50,0:21:55.88,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}模糊的話語在空中消散
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.00,0:21:59.19,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}我明明知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.38,0:22:02.58,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}今天卻還是許下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.81,0:22:09.10,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}無法實現的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.18,0:22:14.41,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}不要鬆開
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.53,0:22:19.23,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}緊緊地 交握雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:25.57,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}說會永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.14,0:22:35.57,song_CN_ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fade(200,200)\an2}緊握的手依然溫暖
